d 1=\"\" style=\" width: 244.72022160665px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар: </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Даъвогарнинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 139.54570637119px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 139.54570637119px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 139.54570637119px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 244.72022160665px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Телефон: </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Даъвогарнинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Электрон почта манзили: </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Даъвогарнинг электрон манзили</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\" width: 139.54570637119px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\" width: 139.54570637119px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\" width: 139.54570637119px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\" width: 244.72022160665px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Жавобгар:</span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Жавобгарнинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\" width: 139.54570637119px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\" width: 139.54570637119px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\" width: 139.54570637119px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\" width: 244.72022160665px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Жавобгарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Телефон: </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Жавобгарнинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Электрон почта манзили: </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Жавобгарнинг электрон манзили</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">ДАЪВО АРИЗА</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Алимент ундириш ҳақида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Мен ва жавобгар ўртамиздаги қонуний никоҳ </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Никоҳ қайд қилинган ФҲДЁ органи номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Никоҳ қайд қилинган вақт</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> куни </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Никоҳни қайд этиш далолатномаси рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> -сон билан қайд этилган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\"\"><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Алимент ундиришга асос бўлган ҳолатлар баён этилади</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Жавобгар моддий таъминламаяпти.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўртамизда алимент тўлаш тўғрисида келишув мавжуд эмас.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Юқоридагиларга кўра, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Оила Кодексининг 117-моддасига асосан </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">СЎРАЙМАН:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Моддий таъминотим учун </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#19}Жавобгарнинг туғилган вақти</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да туғилган жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Жавобгарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">дан ҳар ойда пул билан тўланадиган қатъий </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#20}Талаб қилинаётган алимент миқдори</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> сўм суммасида алимент ундиришни.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Илова: </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#21}Илова қилинаётган ҳужжатлар номи</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#6}Даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 377.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\"> </span></p>\n</div></div>",
